            <bug_when>2009-10-13 16:45:15 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>If a widget with native scrollbars is hidden and then shown again the scrollbar is moved back to the top.

This can be reproduced e.g. in the API viewer:

1. open &lt;http://demo.qooxdoo.org/devel/apiviewer/&gt;
2. open tree folders until a scroll bar is shown in the tree
3. scroll to the bottom
4. Go to the &quot;search&quot; tab
5. go back to the &quot;content&quot; tab

The scroll bar is back at the top.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
